  <thing-type id="evolve_lfm20_00_000" listed="false">
    <label>LFM-20</label>
    <description>&lt;br /&gt&lt;h1&gtOverview&lt;/h1&gt&lt;p&gtRadio Frequency (RF) Controlled, 120 VAC, Scene Capable, Isolated Contact Fixture Module&lt;/p&gt &lt;br /&gt&lt;h2&gtInclusion Information&lt;/h2&gt&lt;p&gtÂ Tap the button.&lt;/p&gt &lt;br /&gt&lt;h2&gtExclusion Information&lt;/h2&gt&lt;p&gtTap the button 3 times, then press and hold (Ex. tap, tap, tap, hold)&lt;/p&gt</description>
